{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"We invent."},{"time":2000,"text":"My company invents"},{"time":4000,"text":"all kinds of new technology"},{"time":6000,"text":"in lots of different areas."},{"time":8000,"text":"And we do that for a couple of reasons."},{"time":10000,"text":"We invent for fun --"},{"time":12000,"text":"invention is a lot of fun to do --"},{"time":15000,"text":"and we also invent for profit."},{"time":17000,"text":"The two are related because"},{"time":19000,"text":"the profit actually takes long enough that if it isn't fun,"},{"time":21000,"text":"you wouldn't have the time to do it."},{"time":23000,"text":"So we do this"},{"time":25000,"text":"fun and profit-oriented inventing"},{"time":27000,"text":"for most of what we do,"},{"time":29000,"text":"but we also have a program where we invent for humanity --"},{"time":32000,"text":"where we take some of our best inventors,"},{"time":34000,"text":"and we say, \"Are there problems"},{"time":36000,"text":"where we have a good idea for solving a problem the world has?\" --"},{"time":39000,"text":"and to solve it in the way we try to solve problems,"},{"time":42000,"text":"which is with dramatic, crazy,"},{"time":44000,"text":"out-of-the-box solutions."},{"time":46000,"text":"Bill Gates is one of those smartest guys of ours"},{"time":48000,"text":"that work on these problems"},{"time":50000,"text":"and he also funds this work, so thank you."},{"time":53000,"text":"So I'm going to briefly discuss"},{"time":55000,"text":"a couple of problems that we have"},{"time":57000,"text":"and a couple of problems where"},{"time":59000,"text":"we've got some solutions underway."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61000,"text":"Vaccination is one of the"},{"time":64000,"text":"key techniques in public health,"},{"time":66000,"text":"a fantastic thing."},{"time":68000,"text":"But in the developing world a lot of vaccines"},{"time":71000,"text":"spoil before they're administered,"},{"time":73000,"text":"and that's because they need to be kept cold."},{"time":76000,"text":"Almost all vaccines need to be kept at refrigerator temperatures."},{"time":79000,"text":"They go bad very quickly if you don't,"},{"time":81000,"text":"and if you don't have stable power grid, this doesn't happen,"},{"time":84000,"text":"so kids die."},{"time":86000,"text":"It's not just the loss of the vaccine that matters;"},{"time":89000,"text":"it's the fact that those kids don't get vaccinated."},{"time":92000,"text":"This is one of the ways that"},{"time":95000,"text":"vaccines are carried:"},{"time":97000,"text":"These are Styrofoam chests. These are being carried by people,"},{"time":100000,"text":"but they're also put on the backs of pickup trucks."},{"time":102000,"text":"We've got a different solution."},{"time":105000,"text":"Now, one of these Styrofoam chests"},{"time":108000,"text":"will last for about four hours with ice in it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110000,"text":"And we thought, well, that's not really good enough."},{"time":113000,"text":"So we made this thing."},{"time":115000,"text":"This lasts six months with no power;"},{"time":118000,"text":"absolutely zero power,"},{"time":120000,"text":"because it loses less"},{"time":122000,"text":"than a half a watt."},{"time":124000,"text":"Now, this is our second generations prototype."},{"time":127000,"text":"The third generation prototype is, right now,"},{"time":129000,"text":"in Uganda being tested."},{"time":132000,"text":"Now, the reason we were able to come up with this"},{"time":134000,"text":"is two key ideas:"},{"time":136000,"text":"One is that this is similar to a cryogenic Dewar,"},{"time":138000,"text":"something you'd keep liquid nitrogen or liquid helium in."},{"time":141000,"text":"They have incredible insulation,"},{"time":143000,"text":"so let's put some incredible insulation here."},{"time":145000,"text":"The other idea is kind of interesting,"},{"time":148000,"text":"which is, you can't reach inside anymore."},{"time":151000,"text":"Because if you open it up and reach inside,"},{"time":153000,"text":"you'd let the heat in, the game would be over."},{"time":155000,"text":"So the inside of this thing actually looks like a Coke machine."},{"time":158000,"text":"It vends out little individual vials."},{"time":161000,"text":"So a simple idea,"},{"time":163000,"text":"which we hope is going to change the way vaccines are distributed"},{"time":166000,"text":"in Africa and around the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":169000,"text":"We'll move on to malaria."},{"time":171000,"text":"Malaria is one of the great public health problems."},{"time":174000,"text":"Esther Duflo talked a little bit about this."},{"time":176000,"text":"Two hundred million people a year."},{"time":179000,"text":"Every 43 seconds a child in Africa dies;"},{"time":183000,"text":"27 will die during my talk."},{"time":188000,"text":"And there's no way for us here in this country"},{"time":191000,"text":"to grasp really what that means to the people involved."},{"time":194000,"text":"Another comment of Esther's"},{"time":196000,"text":"was that we react when there's"},{"time":198000,"text":"a tragedy like Haiti,"},{"time":200000,"text":"but that tragedy is ongoing."},{"time":202000,"text":"So what can we do about it?"},{"time":204000,"text":"Well, there are a lot of things people have tried"},{"time":206000,"text":"for many years for solving malaria."},{"time":208000,"text":"You can spray; the problem is there are environmental issues."},{"time":211000,"text":"You can try to treat people and create awareness."},{"time":214000,"text":"That's great, except the places that have malaria really bad,"},{"time":217000,"text":"they don't have health care systems."},{"time":219000,"text":"A vaccine would be a terrific thing,"},{"time":221000,"text":"only they don't work yet."},{"time":223000,"text":"People have tried for a long time. There are a couple of interesting candidates."},{"time":226000,"text":"It's a very difficult thing to make a vaccine for."},{"time":230000,"text":"You can distribute bed nets,"},{"time":232000,"text":"and bed nets are very effective if you use them."},{"time":235000,"text":"You don't always use them for that. People fish with them."},{"time":237000,"text":"They don't always get to everyone."},{"time":239000,"text":"And bed nets"},{"time":241000,"text":"have an effect on the epidemic,"},{"time":243000,"text":"but you're never going to make it extinct with bed nets."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246000,"text":"Now, malaria is"},{"time":248000,"text":"an incredibly complicated disease."},{"time":251000,"text":"We could spend hours going over this."},{"time":253000,"text":"It's got this sort of soap opera-like lifestyle;"},{"time":255000,"text":"they have sex, they burrow into your liver,"},{"time":258000,"text":"they tunnel into your blood cells ..."},{"time":261000,"text":"it's an incredibly complicated disease,"},{"time":263000,"text":"but that's actually one of the things we find interesting about it"},{"time":266000,"text":"and why we work on malaria:"},{"time":268000,"text":"There's a lot of potential ways in."},{"time":272000,"text":"One of those ways might be better diagnosis."},{"time":275000,"text":"So we hope this year"},{"time":277000,"text":"to prototype each of these devices."},{"time":281000,"text":"One does an automatic malaria diagnosis"},{"time":284000,"text":"in the same way that a diabetic's glucose meter works:"},{"time":287000,"text":"You take a drop of blood,"},{"time":289000,"text":"you put it in there and it automatically tells you."},{"time":291000,"text":"Today, you need to do a complicated laboratory procedure,"},{"time":294000,"text":"create a bunch of microscope slides"},{"time":296000,"text":"and have a trained person examine it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299000,"text":"The other thing is, you know,"},{"time":301000,"text":"it would be even better if you didn't have to draw the blood."},{"time":304000,"text":"And if you look through the eye,"},{"time":306000,"text":"or you look at the vessels on the white of the eye,"},{"time":309000,"text":"in fact, you may be able to do this"},{"time":311000,"text":"directly, without drawing any blood at all,"},{"time":314000,"text":"or through your nail beds."},{"time":316000,"text":"Because if you actually look through your fingernails, you can see blood vessels,"},{"time":319000,"text":"and once you see blood vessels, we think we can see the malaria."},{"time":323000,"text":"We can see it because of this molecule"},{"time":325000,"text":"called hemozoin."},{"time":327000,"text":"It's produced by the malaria parasite"},{"time":330000,"text":"and it's a very interesting crystalline substance."},{"time":334000,"text":"Interesting, anyway, if you're a solid-state physicist."},{"time":336000,"text":"There's a lot of cool stuff we can do with it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339000,"text":"This is our femtosecond laser lab."},{"time":342000,"text":"So this creates pulses of light"},{"time":344000,"text":"that last a femtosecond."},{"time":346000,"text":"That's really, really, really short."},{"time":350000,"text":"This is a pulse of light that's"},{"time":352000,"text":"only about one wavelength of light long,"},{"time":354000,"text":"so it's a whole bunch of photons"},{"time":356000,"text":"all coming and hitting simultaneously."},{"time":358000,"text":"It creates a very high peak power"},{"time":360000,"text":"and it lets you do all kinds of interesting things;"},{"time":362000,"text":"in particular, it lets you find hemozoin."},{"time":364000,"text":"So here's an image of red blood cells,"},{"time":367000,"text":"and now we can actually map"},{"time":369000,"text":"where the hemozoin and where the malaria parasites are"},{"time":372000,"text":"inside those red blood cells."},{"time":374000,"text":"And using both this technique"},{"time":376000,"text":"and other optical techniques,"},{"time":378000,"text":"we think we can make those diagnostics."},{"time":380000,"text":"We also have another hemozoin-oriented"},{"time":382000,"text":"therapy for malaria:"},{"time":384000,"text":"a way, in acute cases, to actually"},{"time":386000,"text":"take the malaria parasite and filter it out of the blood system."},{"time":389000,"text":"Sort of like doing dialysis,"},{"time":391000,"text":"but for relieving the parasite load."}]},{"cues":[{"time":394000,"text":"This is our thousand-core supercomputer."},{"time":397000,"text":"We're kind of software guys,"},{"time":399000,"text":"and so nearly any problem that you pose,"},{"time":402000,"text":"we like to try to solve with some software."},{"time":405000,"text":"One of the problems that you have if you're trying to eradicate malaria"},{"time":408000,"text":"or reduce it"},{"time":410000,"text":"is you don't know what's the most effective thing to do."},{"time":413000,"text":"Okay, we heard about bed nets earlier."},{"time":415000,"text":"You spend a certain amount per bed net."},{"time":417000,"text":"Or you could spray."},{"time":419000,"text":"You can give drug administration."},{"time":421000,"text":"There's all these different interventions"},{"time":423000,"text":"but they have different kinds of effectiveness."},{"time":425000,"text":"How can you tell?"},{"time":427000,"text":"So we've created, using our supercomputer,"},{"time":429000,"text":"the world's best computer model of malaria,"},{"time":431000,"text":"which we'll show you now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":434000,"text":"We picked Madagascar."},{"time":437000,"text":"We have every road,"},{"time":439000,"text":"every village,"},{"time":441000,"text":"every, almost, square inch of Madagascar."},{"time":444000,"text":"We have all of the precipitation data"},{"time":447000,"text":"and the temperature data."},{"time":449000,"text":"That's very important because the humidity and precipitation"},{"time":452000,"text":"tell you whether you've got"},{"time":454000,"text":"standing pools of water for the mosquitoes to breed."},{"time":457000,"text":"So that sets the stage on which you do this."},{"time":460000,"text":"You then have to introduce the mosquitoes,"},{"time":462000,"text":"and you have to model that"},{"time":464000,"text":"and how they come and go."},{"time":466000,"text":"Ultimately, it gives you this."},{"time":468000,"text":"This is malaria spreading"},{"time":470000,"text":"across Madagascar."},{"time":472000,"text":"And this is this latter part of the rainy season."},{"time":475000,"text":"We're going to the dry season now."},{"time":477000,"text":"It nearly goes away in the dry season,"},{"time":479000,"text":"because there's no place for the mosquitoes to breed."},{"time":482000,"text":"And then, of course, the next year it comes roaring back."},{"time":486000,"text":"By doing these kinds of simulations,"},{"time":489000,"text":"we want to eradicate or control malaria"},{"time":491000,"text":"thousands of times in software"},{"time":494000,"text":"before we actually have to do it in real life;"},{"time":497000,"text":"to be able to simulate both the economic trade-offs --"},{"time":500000,"text":"how many bed nets versus how much spraying? --"},{"time":503000,"text":"or the social trade-offs --"},{"time":505000,"text":"what happens if unrest breaks out?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":508000,"text":"We also try to study our foe."},{"time":510000,"text":"This is a high-speed camera view"},{"time":512000,"text":"of a mosquito."},{"time":515000,"text":"And, in a moment,"},{"time":517000,"text":"we're going to see a view of the airflow."},{"time":520000,"text":"Here, we're trying to visualize the airflow"},{"time":522000,"text":"around the wings of the mosquito"},{"time":524000,"text":"with little particles we're illuminating with a laser."},{"time":527000,"text":"By understanding how mosquitoes fly,"},{"time":529000,"text":"we hope to understand how to make them not fly."},{"time":532000,"text":"Now, one of the ways you can make them not fly"},{"time":534000,"text":"is with DDT."},{"time":536000,"text":"This is a real ad."},{"time":538000,"text":"This is one of those things you just can't make up."},{"time":541000,"text":"Once upon a time, this was the primary technique,"},{"time":544000,"text":"and, in fact, many countries got rid of malaria through DDT."},{"time":547000,"text":"The United States did."},{"time":549000,"text":"In 1935, there were 150,000 cases a year"},{"time":552000,"text":"of malaria in the United States,"},{"time":555000,"text":"but DDT and a massive public health effort"},{"time":557000,"text":"managed to squelch it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":560000,"text":"So we thought,"},{"time":562000,"text":"\"Well, we've done all these things that are focused on the Plasmodium,"},{"time":565000,"text":"the parasite involved."},{"time":567000,"text":"What can we do to the mosquito?"},{"time":569000,"text":"Well, let's try to kill it with consumer electronics.\""},{"time":573000,"text":"Now, that sounds silly,"},{"time":575000,"text":"but each of these devices"},{"time":577000,"text":"has something interesting in it that maybe you could use."},{"time":580000,"text":"Your Blu-ray player has"},{"time":582000,"text":"a very cheap blue laser."},{"time":584000,"text":"Your laser printer has a mirror galvanometer"},{"time":586000,"text":"that's used to steer a laser beam very accurately;"},{"time":589000,"text":"that's what makes those little dots on the page."},{"time":592000,"text":"And, of course, there's signal processing"},{"time":594000,"text":"and digital cameras."},{"time":596000,"text":"So what if we could put all that together"},{"time":599000,"text":"to shoot them out of the sky with lasers?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":602000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":604000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":607000,"text":"Now, in our company, this is what we call"},{"time":610000,"text":"\"the pinky-suck moment.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":612000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":614000,"text":"What if we could do that?"},{"time":616000,"text":"Now, just suspend disbelief for a moment,"},{"time":619000,"text":"and let's think of what could happen"},{"time":621000,"text":"if we could do that."},{"time":623000,"text":"Well, we could protect very high-value targets like clinics."},{"time":626000,"text":"Clinics are full of people that have malaria."},{"time":629000,"text":"They're sick, and so they're less able to defend themselves from the mosquitoes."},{"time":632000,"text":"You really want to protect them."},{"time":634000,"text":"Of course, if you do that,"},{"time":636000,"text":"you could also protect your backyard."},{"time":638000,"text":"And farmers could protect their crops"},{"time":640000,"text":"that they want to sell to Whole Foods"},{"time":642000,"text":"because our photons"},{"time":644000,"text":"are 100 percent organic. (Laughter)"},{"time":646000,"text":"They're completely natural."}]},{"cues":[{"time":649000,"text":"Now, it actually gets better than this."},{"time":651000,"text":"You could, if you're really smart,"},{"time":654000,"text":"you could shine a nonlethal laser on the bug"},{"time":657000,"text":"before you zap it,"},{"time":659000,"text":"and you could listen to the wing beat frequency"},{"time":661000,"text":"and you could measure the size."},{"time":663000,"text":"And then you could decide:"},{"time":665000,"text":"\"Is this an insect I want to kill,"},{"time":667000,"text":"or an insect I don't want to kill?\""},{"time":669000,"text":"Moore's law made computing cheap;"},{"time":671000,"text":"so cheap we can weigh"},{"time":673000,"text":"the life of an individual insect"},{"time":675000,"text":"and decide thumbs up"},{"time":678000,"text":"or thumbs down. (Laughter)"},{"time":681000,"text":"Now, it turns out we only kill the female mosquitoes."},{"time":684000,"text":"They're the only ones that are dangerous."},{"time":686000,"text":"Mosquitoes only drink blood"},{"time":688000,"text":"to lay eggs."},{"time":690000,"text":"Mosquitoes actually live ... their day-to-day nutrition"},{"time":693000,"text":"comes from nectar, from flowers --"},{"time":695000,"text":"in fact, in the lab, we feed ours raisins --"},{"time":698000,"text":"but the female needs the blood meal."},{"time":701000,"text":"So, this sounds really crazy, right?"},{"time":703000,"text":"Would you like to see it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":705000,"text":"Audience: Yeah!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":707000,"text":"Nathan Myhrvold: Okay, so our legal department prepared a disclaimer,"},{"time":711000,"text":"and here it is."},{"time":713000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":718000,"text":"Now, after thinking about this a little bit"},{"time":721000,"text":"we thought, you know, it probably would be simpler"},{"time":723000,"text":"to do this with a nonlethal laser."},{"time":725000,"text":"So, Eric Johanson, who built the device,"},{"time":728000,"text":"actually, with parts from eBay;"},{"time":730000,"text":"and Pablos Holman over here,"},{"time":732000,"text":"he's got mosquitoes in the tank."},{"time":734000,"text":"We have the device over here."},{"time":736000,"text":"And we're going to show you,"},{"time":738000,"text":"instead of the kill laser,"},{"time":740000,"text":"which will be a very brief, instantaneous pulse,"},{"time":742000,"text":"we're going to have a green laser pointer"},{"time":744000,"text":"that's going to stay on the mosquito for, actually, quite a long period of time;"},{"time":747000,"text":"otherwise, you can't see it very well."},{"time":749000,"text":"Take it away Eric."}]},{"cues":[{"time":751000,"text":"Eric Johanson: What we have here"},{"time":753000,"text":"is a tank on the other side of the stage."},{"time":755000,"text":"And we have ... this computer screen"},{"time":757000,"text":"can actually see the mosquitoes as they fly around."},{"time":759000,"text":"And Pablos, if he stirs up our mosquitoes a little bit"},{"time":762000,"text":"we can see them flying around."},{"time":764000,"text":"Now, that's a fairly straightforward image processing routine,"},{"time":766000,"text":"and let me show you how it works."},{"time":768000,"text":"Here you can see that the insects are being tracked"},{"time":770000,"text":"as they're flying around,"},{"time":772000,"text":"which is kind of fun."},{"time":775000,"text":"Next we can actually light them up with a laser. (Laughter)"},{"time":777000,"text":"Now, this is a low powered laser,"},{"time":779000,"text":"and we can actually pick up a wing-beat frequency."},{"time":781000,"text":"So you may be able to hear some mosquitoes flying around."}]},{"cues":[{"time":784000,"text":"NM: That's a mosquito wing beat you're hearing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":789000,"text":"EJ: Finally, let's see what this looks like."},{"time":794000,"text":"There you can see mosquitoes as they fly around, being lit up."},{"time":797000,"text":"This is slowed way down"},{"time":799000,"text":"so that you have an opportunity to see what's happening."},{"time":801000,"text":"Here we have it running at high-speed mode."},{"time":803000,"text":"So this system that was built for TED is here to illustrate"},{"time":805000,"text":"that it is technically possible to actually deploy a system like this,"},{"time":808000,"text":"and we're looking very hard at how to make it"},{"time":811000,"text":"highly cost-effective to use in places like Africa and other parts of the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":814000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":821000,"text":"NM: So it wouldn't be any fun to show you that"},{"time":824000,"text":"without showing you what actually happens when we hit 'em."},{"time":827000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":835000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":838000,"text":"This is very satisfying."},{"time":840000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":843000,"text":"This is one of the first ones we did."},{"time":845000,"text":"The energy's a little bit high here."},{"time":847000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":852000,"text":"We'll loop around here in just a second, and you'll see another one."},{"time":854000,"text":"Here's another one. Bang."},{"time":856000,"text":"An interesting thing is, we kill them all the time;"},{"time":859000,"text":"we've never actually gotten the wings to shut off in midair."},{"time":862000,"text":"The wing motor is very resilient."},{"time":864000,"text":"I mean, here we're blowing wings off"},{"time":866000,"text":"but the wing motor keeps all the way down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":870000,"text":"So, that's what I have. Thanks very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":872000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}